text:
Empowering you with data-driven solutions




I deliver data solutions that save time, reduce errors, and unlock insights.
Whether you’re a researcher, a data team, or a tech department, I help turn complex datasets into clear, actionable outcomes.






 For Researchers & Analysts


Faster publications, cleaner data, less manual work.

+ More details

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Automated data collection from APIs, databases, and online sources&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Cleaning, correction, and transformation into publication-ready datasets&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Bibliometric & scientometric analysis for research evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Automated manuscript writing with &lt;strong&gt;R + Quarto&lt;/strong&gt; (Zotero integration, reproducible workflows)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Examples: Assisted researchers with automated PubMed data extraction and created reproducible Quarto manuscripts ready for submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;






 For Data Professionals


Reliable pipelines, accurate migrations, better decisions.

+ More details

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;ETL pipelines for healthcare and pharma data&lt;/li&gt;
